  <span id="freeText10941540022486982866" style="display:none">"Whether a man is a legend or not is decided by history, not fortune tellers."<br /><br />Books can take you to a different world and honestly speaking ShivaTrilogy is that kind of book series.<br />It was the first book series I ever read and now it's one of my favourite book series. A book that can't be kept down in between the pages. <br />The trilogy is a mix of fictional mythology, fantasy, action, thriller, drama, science and passionate love. I was imagining the characters, the cities, the wars and I never felt less excited a single moment throughout the reading. The entire series engages the reader in such a way that one cannot help but get involved with the characters.</span>
