<div id="review_2034600214" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2034600214" />
    <a title="Mallika Rathore" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/68753909-mallika-rathore"><img alt="Mallika Rathore" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1501988216p2/68753909.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2034600214?book_show_action=true">Jun 19, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Mallika Rathore" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Mallika Rathore" href="/user/show/68753909-mallika-rathore">Mallika Rathore</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/68753909-mallika-rathore?shelf=read_2017">read_2017</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/68753909-mallika-rathore?shelf=indian">indian</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2034600214" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3313824537595628707">Despite all the amazing reviews this series had, I was very skeptical about reading it because of my disappointment with other Indian authors; but I am glad I finally read it. It provided a different perspective to the one of the greatest tales in Indian mythology, which is very refreshing! It does not really deviate from the stories we all grew up with, but still is unique in it&apos;s own way.</span>
  <span id="freeText3313824537595628707" style="display:none">Despite all the amazing reviews this series had, I was very skeptical about reading it because of my disappointment with other Indian authors; but I am glad I finally read it. It provided a different perspective to the one of the greatest tales in Indian mythology, which is very refreshing! It does not really deviate from the stories we all grew up with, but still is unique in it's own way.</span>
  <a data-text-id="3313824537595628707" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


